    <item>
      <title>Solution of Inside problem is not outside</title>
      <link>/wiaposts/solution-of-inside-problem-is-not-outside/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 08:33:00 +0530</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>/wiaposts/solution-of-inside-problem-is-not-outside/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/assets/images/wiapost/5256-Solution-of-Inside-problem-is-not-outside.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Solution of Inside problem is not outside&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Solution of Inside Problem is not Outside 
    &lt;div id=&#34;solution-of-inside-problem-is-not-outside&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#solution-of-inside-problem-is-not-outside&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When your mind is weary, burdened and low,&lt;br&gt;
Defeated, exhausted, where do you go?&lt;br&gt;
Lonely, sad, with shadows that cling,&lt;br&gt;
You know this life is not the song you sing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;But who is it, this &amp;ldquo;you&amp;rdquo; who feels the pain,&lt;br&gt;
Who yearns for peace, to be whole again?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
